# Cost & compliance guardrails

## Cost — keep near $0
- No NAT Gateway, no VPC-attached Lambdas, no always-on containers (ECS/EKS/RDS).
- DynamoDB on-demand; CloudWatch log retention **7 days**; SES **sandbox** only.
- No custom domain / Route53 until explicitly requested (avoids fixed monthly fee).
- Prefer SnapStart over provisioned concurrency for Java.

## Demo vs real launch
| Demo does | Real launch needs |
|-----------|-------------------|
| Mock providers / slots | Credentialed CRM doctors + video |
| Watermarked Rx PDF + placeholders | ICP-Brasil NGS2 + SNCR API |
| Rules-based BMI/comorbidity scoring | Medical-director protocol |
| Plans UI only (no payments) | PIX Automático + cards |
| SES email | WhatsApp Business primary |
| Consent records + sa-east-1 posture in docs | DPO, RIPD, ANPD processes |

## Regulatory keywords (cite, do not invent)
Lei 14.510/2022, CFM 2.314/2022, CFM 2.299/2021, ANVISA RDC 873/2024 + RDC 1.000/2025 (SNCR), LGPD art. 5/11. Competitors for narrative: Liti, Farmex, Manual vs MEDVi US.

UI and API copy must stay PT-BR-first with explicit **demonstração / portfolio** disclaimers.
